patthana14.23:4.1: Cetasikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacetasiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:4.2: Hetuyā nava … pe … purejāte āsevane pañca … pe … avigate nava.
patthana14.23:5.1: Cittasampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasampayutto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe ….
patthana14.23:6.1: Cittasaṃsaṭṭhaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasaṃsaṭṭho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:7.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā pañca … pe … aññamaññe cha, purejāte āsevane ekaṃ … pe … avigate nava.
patthana14.23:8.1: Cittasamuṭṭhānaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasamuṭṭhāno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:9.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā pañca … pe … purejāte āsevane pañca … pe … avigate nava.
patthana14.23:10.1: Cittasahabhuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasahabhū dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe …
patthana14.23:10.3: cittānuparivattiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittānuparivattī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe …
patthana14.23:10.5: cittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhāno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe …
patthana14.23:10.7: cittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānasahabhū dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe …
patthana14.23:10.9: cittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānānuparivattiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nacittasaṃsaṭṭhasamuṭṭhānānuparivattī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:11.1: Hetuyā nava … pe … purejāte āsevane pañca … pe … avigate nava.
patthana14.23:12.1: Ajjhattikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.23:13.1: Bāhiraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.23:14.1: Ajjhattikañca bāhirañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.23:15.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe pañca, adhipatiyā pañca … pe … purejāte āsevane pañca … pe … avigate nava.
patthana14.23:16.1: Upādā dhammaṃ paṭicca noupādā dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.23:17.1: Noupādā dhammaṃ paṭicca nanoupādā dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.23:18.1: Upādā ca noupādā ca dhammaṃ paṭicca noupādā dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:19.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā tīṇi … pe … purejāte āsevane ekaṃ … pe … avigate pañca.
patthana14.23:20.1: Upādinnaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naupādinno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana14.23:21.1: Anupādinnaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanupādinno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.23:22.1: Upādinnañca anupādinnañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naupādinno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.23:23.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā ekaṃ … pe … āsevane ekaṃ … pe … avigate pañca.
